--Differences between AWS VPC and GCP VPC

1. Scope of VPC: 
AWS : regional
GCP : Global

2.subnet design:
AWS : zonal 
GCP : regional

3. IP range:
AWS : you define the CIDR ----> vpc --> 10.0.0.0/16   10.1.0.0/24
GCP : works on mode --> Auto and Custome

4. Internet access:
AWS: igw, nat gateway
GCP : cloud NAT, igw 

5.security:
AWS : SG, NACL 
GCP : Firewall                        tags: https 


